{
  "stem": "25639.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And so mother was given a strong reprimand, that if she'll ever do this again, she will never come out alive from what she will receive as a result.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And so mother gratefully was returned to Anushka and me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I was there, too, but the kapo didn't mention me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "This was-- there was a reason for it, I'm sure.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, thank you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know I started that, and I overlooked that story.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One day, we had to remove all our clothes after we worked.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a total surprise.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That-- this was the first time-- and-- for an inspection.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Shoes, everything, had to be removed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so, well, we didn't have much clothes on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had a dress on and the shoes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so we had to remove the dress.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had to remove his shoes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we were really-- this time we were totally naked.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I got-- I got so worried, and mother came over and, looking some-- in another direction, said, please pretend you know nothing about the diamond.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I said, mother, you're going to have to get rid of it, or-- or we're going to lose you.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she-- she said, I will-- I will do it my way.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And so she picked up a-- a-- actually didn't pick it up, but with the toes of her shoes, before she took it off, she created a little hole there.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then she took off her shoe, that shoe, the right shoe, and she turned it upside down and sort of dropped it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And while she was removing her other shoe, she moved the pebble over the diamond.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I really took a-- I did a sigh of relief.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
